{"tid":458474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(求向FIFA投訴template) 鄰國球迷足球場內狂噓南韓國歌!!!!!!","createTime":"2017-11-05T01:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T10:36:18.000Z","uid":136994,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3b70a777fc90760cd851b3305ad8a16375b2b36d","tid":458474,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T01:51:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20170323/1083078/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20170323%2F1083078%2F&d=7KkDAQFqj8%2BYkqHEThfTyQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=2ea17194\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20170323%2F1083078%2F&h=17e08cb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20170323/1083078/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國國家隊今晚在湖南長沙迎戰南韓隊，進行2018俄羅斯世界盃的外圍賽。賽事開始奏南韓國歌時，場內的中國球迷不斷發出噓聲和吹哨聲。<br />\n <br />\n微博網友貼文說「剛剛奏韓國國歌時，全場都在噓和吹哨兒！」不少網友都大罵當地球迷：「韓國國歌一片噓聲，長沙智障還是多！」「長沙這麼噓&hellip;&hellip;到底是敏感時期&hellip;&hellip;」「這個國的民族自豪就是這樣培養起來的，shame on you！」<br />\n<br />\n「在其他國家奏國歌的時候連基本的尊重都沒有嗎？​」<br />\n<br />\n「奏韓國國歌，噓聲，吼聲四起，已經輸了，丟人啊！」<br />\n <br />\n「這麼噓別人的國歌，還喊『棒子』，太丟人了，賽後估計還得被罰！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然蝗同泡都係五十百笑百步㗎啦<br />\n不過班蝗咁介意人噓國歌，自己又噓人地國歌<br />\n唔知道有冇人可以諗吓點draft向FIFA投訴template<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想睇鄰國隊閉門作賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61571f25f22f9d8d09a920b1a4d6c93da6260b17","tid":458474,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T01:52:35.000Z","msg":"第 1 頁<br />\n#1狗鐵馬屎坑 &bull; 44s<br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20170323/1083078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20170323%2F1083078&d=7KkDAQFqj8%2BYkqHEThfTyQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=330bd85b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.